Package: ggupset
Title: Clean, Modifiable Upset Plots Using ggplot2 and Patchwork
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", email = "you@email.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Builds upset plots as independently-themeable ggplot2 panels
    assembled with patchwork. Each panel (intersection bars, membership
    matrix, optional set-size bars) is a plain ggplot2 object, making
    aesthetic customization consistent with standard ggplot2 idioms.
